*Večeras* ću ići u bioskop. (Tonight I'm going to the movies.)

*Večeras* ćemo provesti vreme zajedno. (Tonight we'll spend time together.)

*Večeras* ću napraviti nešto posebno za tebe. (Tonight I'll do something special for you.)

Moja mama *večeras* neće biti kod kuće. (My mom won't be home tonight.)

*Večeras* ćemo gledati film. (Tonight we'll watch a movie.)

*Večeras* ću se vratiti kući kasno. (Tonight I'll be back home late.)